snippet.title: Black Squad l Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Black Squad is a free-to-play military first-person-shooter on Steam. With a range of game maps, modes and weapons to choose from, players can master their skills and show off their strategies. 

Play Black Squad now for free!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/550650/Black_Squad/

Find out more:
• Website: http://blacksquad.com/
• Discord: https://discord.gg/blacksquad 
• Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/playblacksquad/
• Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayBlackSquad
• Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/blacksquadonline
